Class User

java.lang.Object
co.edu.unbosque.proyectocalendar.model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
@Entity public class User extends Object implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
Representa un usuario del sistema y es compatible con Spring Security al implementar la interfaz UserDetails.
